[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0027","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0027.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0029","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9103,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10789}}","description":"tags.<value>UnixWare 系统中的 pis 和 mkpis 命令存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地低权限用户可通过创建指向系统敏感文件的符号链接，当这些命令以高权限运行时，攻击者利用该漏洞可覆盖或篡改关键系统文件，从而实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 UnixWare 操作系统，攻击者需要具备本地访问权限才能成功利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级为中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0029"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:51.333","remediation":"安装 SCO 发布的最新 UnixWare 安全补丁，并更新或移除 Skunkware 中的 orion 软件包（含 pis 和 mkpis 命令）。具体操作：首先通过 `patchadd` 确认系统已安装全部当前可用安全补丁；若无需使用 orion 相关命令，可直接删除或卸载该软件包以消除攻击面；如确有使用需求，请访问 SCO Skunkware 网站获取 orion 更新版本。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份对 pis 和 mkpis 命令设置不可写符号链接的权限保护，限制普通用户的符号链接创建能力，从而阻断利用路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94780294009285&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/901","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/985d46f062894917f05cdf3d64399a32839d12b7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0029.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0029","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0029.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5d448b12fda744aa8491fddc8705260f2b4289f2/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0029.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5bd4fceb27857756215e988f4824b12d3de84ec1/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8m9f-gvrp-3wgm/GHSA-8m9f-gvrp-3wgm.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0029.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fca0a8f0c4e8e363295abb0217269b2593cf1f3b/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0025","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0025.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0027","title":"IBM Network Station Manager 竞争条件权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM Network Station Manager（NetStation）2.0r1 存在竞争条件漏洞，其特权进程在处理临时文件或日志文件时未对文件路径进行严格的符号链接（symlink）检查，导致存在「检查-使用」时间差（TOCTOU）。本地低权限用户可通过在特权进程操作的文件路径处创建符号链接，指向其可控的系统关键文件，在竞争窗口内使特权进程跟随该链接进行写操作，从而覆盖或篡改本应由高权限管理的系统文件，最终实现本地权限提升，获得系统的 root 或管理员级别访问权限。该漏洞影响 IBM Network Station Manager 2.0r1 版本，CVSS v2 评分为 6.2（中危），攻击复杂度较高，需本地账户访问权限即可触发。IBM 建议用户升级至修复版本，并确保特权进程使用 O_NOFOLLOW 等安全机制处理文件操作，防止符号链接攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0027"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:51.093","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM Network Station Manager 2.0 R2 或更高版本，该版本修复了 NetStation 的竞态条件漏洞。如暂无法升级，应以最小权限运行 NetStation 服务，限制本地用户对临时目录的写入权限，并定期审计 /tmp 等可写目录下的符号链接创建行为，避免攻击者通过符号链接攻击提升权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/5381.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/39962","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/900","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19697","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/edbb10deb36e9400fcd245fdb6d1781b6f0ae700/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0027.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0027","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0027.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/af2c3b5adc3ff9dc412f664a188835d908ce9d5f/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0027.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qv8j-42h3-c36j/GHSA-qv8j-42h3-c36j.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0027.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/30840c8fa1a16a55410c671ff85fbfa95b4cbcfe/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0025.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0011","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0010","title":"Tony Greenwood WebWho+ 1.1 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"WebWho+ 1.1 的 whois.cgi 程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 TLD 参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Tony Greenwood WebWho+ 1.1 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。由于 CGI 程序未对用户输入进行有效过滤，导致攻击者可直接在目标服务器上执行恶意命令，获取系统控制权。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0010"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:49.007","remediation":"立即停用 WebWho+ 1.1 的 whois.cgi 脚本，或彻底移除该 CGI 程序。由于该软件已停止维护且无安全补丁，建议迁移至其他受支持的 Whois 查询工具（如 jwhois 或 whois 命令行工具），并在 Web 服务器层面禁用 CGI 执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0010","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19691","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0010.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0010.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0010","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/55a3ad339a88e525c3ea8b8880b59dff1ae32980/2000/CVE-2000-0010.json","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0010/README.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0010.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jg25-mxp8-jxr3/GHSA-jg25-mxp8-jxr3.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0010.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/webwho_pl.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0009","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0008","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9101,\"outputTokens\":15,\"totalTokens\":10780}}","description":"FTPPro 客户端将敏感信息以明文形式存储在本地文件中，本地用户可直接读取这些文件获取敏感数据。该漏洞源于程序未对存储的认证凭据、配置信息等敏感数据进行加密保护，导致拥有本地系统访问权限的攻击者可通过文件系统直接查看明文内容。攻击条件要求攻击者已具备目标主机的本地登录权限，利用方式为遍历 FTPPro 配置目录读取存储敏感信息的文件。漏洞影响 FTPPro 所有受影响版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，属于低危本地信息泄露漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0008"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:48.760","remediation":"升级 FTPPro 至官方已修复的后续版本（建议联系厂商获取 2000 年后发布的安全版本），并将软件存储的敏感信息由明文改为加密保存。在无法立即升级时，应限制 FTPPro 所在主机的本地用户访问权限，使用文件系统权限（如 chmod 600）收紧配置文件读写范围，避免非授权用户读取明文敏感数据。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0008","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0008.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d3c24daa4de56d2cb70c1fd2d4f8d5a03642400e/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0008.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0008","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/c65aa0025d86dea25f44e3bc22e827ebe0ffe3a2/2000/CVE-2000-0008.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0008.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2a1a519e4e9d3e489c2169e3db04269b559dd18e/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0008.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1790/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--02e47c55-93fc-4f6f-853f-d254db309896.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0007","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0006","title":"strace strace 本地任意文件读取漏洞","description":"strace 工具在处理内存映射文件名时存在任意文件读取漏洞。本地攻击者可通过 strace 跟踪其他进程的方式，利用内存映射文件名中的路径信息读取系统上任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 strace 工具，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，危害等级较低，CVSS 评分 2.6。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0006"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:48.500","remediation":"升级 strace 至 4.3 及以上版本（修复了通过内存映射文件名读取任意文件的缺陷）。如暂时无法升级，应限制普通用户对 strace 的执行权限（如通过 sudo 规则或移除 setuid），并避免在该系统上以特权用户运行未知程序，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://online.securityfocus.com/archive/1/39831","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4554","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/84f82928c38b4d0e02149dbde07f5affc7f46f43/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0006.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0006","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/11c31a44fb748171baca403be9347d7c6597c891/upstream-layers/openembedded-core/meta/conf/distro/include/cve-extra-exclusions.inc","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0006.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cc528fa33408da88ea19cf3d01d2185cd0ffe95a/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0006.json","https://github.com/joaop9425/manual-do-tecnico/blob/cc6e0f5304777f18e55db554da5372bc31d4cae1/src/content/noticias/2026/01/04/seguranca/cve-2000-0006-strace-allows-local-users-to-read-ar-1767537313000.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fmp9-jf38-4px4/GHSA-fmp9-jf38-4px4.json","https://github.com/openembedded/openembedded-core/blob/171af3b2915dd076c8d1b205ff75eac1ebd5a586/meta/conf/distro/include/cve-extra-exclusions.inc","https://github.com/microsoft/AzureLinuxVulnerabilityData/blob/717b8e86b0e72133c5d0afc2bab7a3302e92b8bd/osv/AZL-35286.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0026","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0028","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨帧安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 与 5.01 版本存在跨框架安全策略绕过漏洞。该漏洞源于浏览器的 external.NavigateAndFind() 函数未正确实施同源与跨框架访问限制，导致远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，在用户访问时利用该函数绕过浏览器的跨框架安全隔离机制，非法读取受害者本地文件系统上的文件内容。攻击条件为攻击者需诱导受害者使用受影响的 IE 版本打开其控制的网页，无需身份认证或本地交互。受影响产品包括 Internet Explorer 4、5、5.01 及 5.5 等多个版本，虽 CVSS 评分较低（2.6），但仍可能导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0028"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-23T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:51.210","remediation":"建议将 Internet Explorer 升级至 5.5 SP2 或更高版本（如 IE 6 及后续版本），以修复 external.NavigateAndFind() 跨帧安全策略绕过漏洞。如短期内无法升级，可临时通过 Internet Options → Security 将 Internet 区域安全级别调至 High，或禁用 Active Scripting 作为缓解措施，并避免访问不受信任的网站。长期而言，建议迁移至现代浏览器以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0028","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19686","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0028.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c707cc2908b5d07c1aaeed7fd0c79e5c6b4bb826/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0028.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0028","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/bfd46727c1a0f7508f02358ff91eaa5d0847d1e4/2000/CVE-2000-0028.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0028.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/aeda8c7b429aa1dfdb16de3b1ae154a7b870f9be/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0028.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000962.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0026.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0026.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0088","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0088.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0040","title":"glFtpD SITE ZIPCHK命令元字符注入权限提升漏洞","description":"glFtpD FTP服务器在处理SITE ZIPCHK命令时未正确过滤用户输入中的元字符（如管道符、分号等），本地用户可通过构造特制参数注入并执行任意系统命令，从而绕过权限限制并提升权限。攻击者需具备本地访问或有效FTP登录能力，成功利用后可完全控制运行该服务的主机，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0040"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-23","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即停用或限制glFtpD的SITE ZIPCHK命令，禁止普通用户执行该SITE扩展；收紧FTP账户权限与本地登录，避免以高权限账号运行服务。该漏洞年代久远且官方公开补丁信息不完整，建议将glFtpD替换为仍在维护的FTP服务（如vsftpd、ProFTPD），并关闭不必要的SITE命令与系统命令调用能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0040","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0040","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19e384b1ab805bcd3bddb9050d2fe43dd342f230/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0040.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0088.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0077","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0077.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0038","title":"glFTPd 1.17.2 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"glFTPd 1.17.2 FTP 服务器存在默认账户漏洞，软件内置了名为 glftpd 的默认用户账户，该账户使用固定默认密码且 UID 被设置为 0（超级管理员权限）。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 FTP 协议登录该默认账户，直接获取目标系统的 root 级完全控制权限，进而执行任意命令、上传恶意文件或窃取敏感数据。该漏洞影响 glFTPd 1.17.2 及更早版本，攻击复杂度低，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0038"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-23","updated":"1999-12-23","remediation":"立即删除 glFTPd 中默认的 glftpd 系统账户（UID 0，密码为默认值），或升级至已修复此问题的 glFTPd 1.17.3 及以上版本。如无法升级，建议在 ftpusers 文件中禁止 root 用户登录，并改用 vsftpd 或 Pure-FTPd 等持续维护的 FTP 服务替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19690","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0038.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5546763f2cbf8b9d0a5bd1b009f21d50c3edeb8b/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0038.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0038","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/c913d7ecf9e9819db89a5ce38cea430246095002/2000/CVE-2000-0038.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0038.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1eab609178bfac1fdc1fdc37b8b4d17d9ecf98b7/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0038.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88216/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ec3be0baed1eb129c466b944014a0769e187fd54/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0077.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0003","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0001","title":"RealNetworks RealServer 5.0 ramgen 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"RealNetworks RealServer 5.0 的 ramgen 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 ramgen 请求触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 RealServer 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0001"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-23","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 RealNetworks RealServer 至 5.0.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 ramgen 组件对超长请求的处理逻辑。若产品已停止支持，建议迁移至替代流媒体服务器方案，并在网络边界配置 WAF 规则或反向代理，限制请求 URI 长度不超过 4096 字节以缓解攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/888","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19687"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0003.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0003.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0104","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0119","title":"McAfee Virus Scan 和 Norton Anti-Virus 回收站文件夹扫描绕过漏洞","description":"McAfee Virus Scan 与 Norton Anti-Virus 等杀毒软件的默认配置未将 Windows 回收站文件夹（RECYCLED）纳入病毒扫描范围，攻击者可将恶意代码存放于回收站目录中，绕过杀毒软件的实时监控与文件扫描检测。该漏洞影响 McAfee 4.0、Network Associates for Windows NT 4.0.2/4.0.3a 及 Norton AntiVirus 2000 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者无需特殊权限，只需将恶意文件写入回收站即可实现免杀存放，后续通过其他方式诱导用户执行即可完成攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0119"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:02.397","remediation":"在 McAfee VirusScan 中手动添加 RECYCLED 文件夹到扫描范围，或升级至支持回收站扫描的后续版本；Norton AntiVirus 2000 用户应升级到 Norton AntiVirus 2001 或更高版本，其默认配置已包含回收站扫描。如无法升级，创建自定义扫描策略将 `C:\\RECYCLED` 和 `C:\\RECYCLER` 目录加入实时监控路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94936267131123&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19733","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0119.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0119.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0119","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0119.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0119.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8ffx-cmw4-hwwr/GHSA-8ffx-cmw4-hwwr.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0119.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/956/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0066","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0066.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0032","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10813,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10833}}","description":"Solaris 7.0 的 DMI（桌面管理接口）组件中存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 /var/dmi/db 数据库目录中添加特制的恶意文件，触发 dmispd 守护进程崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 操作系统，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，无需高权限即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0032"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:51.683","remediation":"建议升级到 Sun Solaris 7_x86 推荐的维护补丁簇（如 106541-05 及以上，对应 SPARC 平台 106541 系列补丁），或通过 SunSolve 安装 dmispd 相关的最新内核/系统补丁。如无法立即打补丁，可暂时将 /var/dmi/db 目录权限收紧为仅 root 可写（chmod 700 /var/dmi/db 并校验属主），并移除普通用户的写权限以阻止写入畸形文件触发 dmispd 崩溃，同时可通过 RBAC 限制非授权用户访问 DMI 数据库作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7582","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/878","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19681","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5546763f2cbf8b9d0a5bd1b009f21d50c3edeb8b/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0032.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0032","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0032/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0032.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/aeda8c7b429aa1dfdb16de3b1ae154a7b870f9be/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0032.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4qj3-rmh9-cc9v/GHSA-4qj3-rmh9-cc9v.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0032.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d1825faa-5f7d-45f8-b00d-8c89cfa8e56a.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0066.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0066.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0066.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0034","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0034.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0036","title":"Microsoft Outlook Express 5 for Macintosh HTML 邮件附件自动下载漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook Express 5 for Macintosh 在处理 HTML 格式电子邮件时存在安全缺陷，当收件人打开包含附件的 HTML 邮件时，应用程序会在未经用户任何确认或提示的情况下，自动将邮件附件下载并保存到本地系统中。该漏洞影响运行于 Macintosh 平台的 Outlook Express 5 版本，攻击条件为攻击者只需向目标用户发送一封精心构造的 HTML 邮件即可，无需用户主动点击或执行任何操作。利用方式上，攻击者可借此在用户无感知的情况下将恶意文件投递至本地，为后续社会工程学攻击或恶意代码执行创造前提条件，构成隐私泄露与潜在的安全风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0036"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:52.150","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-060 发布的补丁程序，或升级到 Internet Explorer 5.0 for Macintosh 及更高版本以消除此漏洞。如无法立即安装补丁，可在 Outlook Express 中禁用 HTML 邮件预览功能，改为纯文本阅读模式，以阻止邮件附件自动下载。注意该产品已停止支持，建议迁移至现代邮件客户端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ249082","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-060","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0036.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/60b8b9aa4f79741865e2bfbede0fd6940ac5d90b/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0036.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0036","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0f6f0e28732bc614273e91613aef04def1dce90b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0036.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/938d5f69569a096cf728175efd0ca15f6fd92c6a/README.md","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0036.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b5386010defc8c0fd9ec1ae3d4b050a464f243a4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wh2w-hjg4-rm27/GHSA-wh2w-hjg4-rm27.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/2000/CVE-2000-0036.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a764f258-6b82-4c04-ba90-c93bde670c0a.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0034.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0031","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0031.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0034","title":"Netscape Communicator 密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.7 存在密码明文存储漏洞，当用户通过 IMAP 或 POP 协议收发邮件时，即使未勾选\"记住密码\"选项，程序仍会将用户密码以明文形式记录在 preferences.js 配置文件中。本地攻击者若能访问该文件，即可直接获取用户邮箱凭据，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Netscape 4.7 及可能的相关版本，危害等级中等，需通过升级或手动清理配置文件修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0034"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:51.913","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.7x 或更高版本，该版本修复了密码明文存储问题。如无法升级，使用后手动删除 preferences.js 文件中记录的密码字段，或改用 Thunderbird 等现代邮件客户端替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0034","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/553b36786ea28855fe97ba80cc96d54a735075a3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0034.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0034","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/bc8e516d860e1e416e84f3d37f76b750af4f5377/2000/CVE-2000-0034.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0034.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2df7e2c20081f44b866b16619f1f9253b790f640/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-237w-fwrp-rqvw/GHSA-237w-fwrp-rqvw.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0f6f0e28732bc614273e91613aef04def1dce90b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0034.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88221/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0028","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0028.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0030","title":"Sun Solaris dmispd 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris DMI（桌面管理接口）服务中的 dmispd 组件的 dmi_cmd 命令存在安全漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 /var/dmi/db 数据库目录添加大量文件，耗尽受限磁盘空间，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限，利用门槛较低，可造成系统关键服务因磁盘空间不足而中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0030"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:51.450","remediation":"建议立即停止并禁用 dmispd 服务（/etc/init.d/dmi stop；chkconfig dmi off），限制本地用户对 /var/dmi/db 目录的写入权限（chmod 750 /var/dmi/db），并对 /var 分区设置磁盘配额（edquota）防止单个用户耗尽磁盘空间。如运行 Solaris 7 或更早版本，建议升级至受支持的 Solaris 11 或迁移至 Oracle Solaris 最新发布版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/878","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/985d46f062894917f05cdf3d64399a32839d12b7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0030.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0030","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-2000-0030.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5d448b12fda744aa8491fddc8705260f2b4289f2/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0030.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5bd4fceb27857756215e988f4824b12d3de84ec1/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x2hc-692w-3vgc/GHSA-x2hc-692w-3vgc.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0030.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000957.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d166d3eea7cab7b1622230f2a1a9edfc1f277bf7/2000.tsv","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-2000.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0028.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0016","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0016.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0018","title":"Window Maker wmmon 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统下的 WindowMaker 窗口管理器附属工具 wmmon（1.0 beta 2 版本）在处理用户主目录中的 .wmmonrc 配置文件时存在安全缺陷。该工具会以较高权限读取并执行该配置文件中的指令，因此本地已登录的用户可通过精心构造恶意的 .wmmonrc 文件内容，诱使 wmmon 以特权身份执行攻击者指定的命令，从而从普通用户权限提升为特权用户（如 root）。由于该漏洞仅要求攻击者在目标系统上拥有本地账户并能够写入自身主目录下的配置文件，利用门槛较低，影响所有安装并运行受影响版本 wmmon 的 FreeBSD 系统，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0018"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.007","remediation":"建议立即升级 WindowMaker wmmon 至修复版本（1.0b3 及以上，参见 FreeBSD 安全公告），或移除 setuid 位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/X11R6/bin/wmmon）以阻止其以 root 权限运行。临时缓解措施：删除或限制用户可写的 .wmmonrc 配置文件权限（chmod 644 ~/.wmmonrc），避免本地用户注入命令提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1169","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/885","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19685","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b3f84cd2bd659a86c86b8cfbfca1a01084368c06/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0018","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rq6w-v5p8-7365/GHSA-rq6w-v5p8-7365.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0018.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f95ed58f-e12f-4d60-b42f-eb76b7f6d21f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/30840c8fa1a16a55410c671ff85fbfa95b4cbcfe/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0016.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0016.toml"}]